info.name: Colorado
info.description: COLORADO will let you appreciate the benefits of a large family. COLORADO is big, comfortable and modern, and the units in this collection are designed to seat many people. With the large seats and many cushions, COLORADO will give all your family maximum comfort during family celebrations. The COLORADO family is also impressive – it includes armchairs, sofas and corner sofas available in various sizes and arrangements. COLORADO – family celebrations every day.
